of transfer transaction costs.</p><p>Ethereum or Ripple can be a good alternative here, which many more casinos also accept as payment at the moment. You can actually use Skrill and Neteller to buy cryptocurrencies, and open a separate wallet for crypto transactions if you wish.</p><p>Among other things, Frank Casino and Slot V support payment with cryptocurrency:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4>PayNPlay coming soon?</h4><p>Since 2018, Swedish and Finnish players have had the opportunity to transfer money directly to their favorite games, without a whole lot of complicated registration at new casinos. All verification is via the payment solution if you already have an account with them. So hopefully this service will be available to all European players as well, in that you manage all of the transactions yourself via PaynPlay. Even withdrawals are very fast and you can start playing instantly at another casino. Verification of transactions is also very secure, with Bank ID as standard in Sweden and Finland. Right at this point, we are very jealous of our neighbors in the north ...</p>',	NULL,	NULL,	'Payment solutions to online casinos in Europe!',	'payment, skrill, neteller, paysafecard, trusly, paynplay',	'Read about all the best solutions for payment to online casinos that work for all players in Europe. See whatæs available now, and what you can use in the future!',	'2020-07-13 00:35:08',	'2021-03-08 07:36:04'),
