(57,	'responsible-gaming',	'responsible_gaming_description',	'<p>You\'ve probably seen that every casino on this site has a page they call \"Responsible Gambling\", but what does that mean? This basically means that you have to have a conscious relationship with how much you are playing for and can handle such expense with your daily expenses.</p><p>Unfortunately, too many people today are unaware of exactly this, and allow gambling to slip out until both the house and family are gone. This is definitely something we at Slottomat.com do not want, and so we want to make sure that all our users are aware of how to limit games and stick to a budget.</p><p><strong>What are the signs that you\'re playing too much?</strong></p><p>In the beginning, you may have a clear idea of ​​how much you can play for a month. But as time goes by, the amount begins to grow gradually until you are no longer able to service this hobby.</p><p>The reason for this happening is often that you \"chase\" the losses. It is frustrating to lose money, probably everyone knows it. But even if you realize it, it\'s easy to persuade yourself to play more to recapture the losses.</p><p>Losing money and losing money at casino games can also be very embarrassing to talk about. That\'s why most people hide their gambling problem from friends and family, until it\'s too late. Imagine saying to your spouse that you have wasted both your house, your car and your retirement savings. That is a devastating conversation no one wants.</p><p>If you feel that you are playing too much, grab a hold og yourself now, and don\'t wait until it\'s too late. Of course, there are opportunities to get help even if gambling has completely taken over, but it will take longer time to correct.</p><p><strong>Tips to keep your gambling on the right track</strong></p><p>First and foremost, be aware of how much you can play with for a month, and put restrictions on this. Also, you can take advantage of payment solutions that can help you stick to your budget. Instead of using credit cards or visas that are directly linked to your bank account, rather use visa cards where you have to prepay how much to spend.</p><p>Every casino today has pretty much the opportunity to limit your game. If you do not trust that you can do this yourself, you can put your own barriers in online casinos to help you keep your budget. These barriers cannot be changed in 2 weeks from the date of change. This is to ensure that you do not make the wrong decisions to remove your limits.</p><p>Another thing you should do is to be honest and open about your playing. Do not hide this from your spouse or others close to you. Say that you play occasionally and stick to a budget. Then you will feel far more responsibility around your gambling by also giving a promise to those closest to you not to play too much.</p><p><strong>Contact the helpline</strong></p><p>We at slottomat.com can only give you general advice and guidance on this topic, so unfortunately we don\'t have all the answers. Therefore, you should contact these websites below if you fell you have a gambling problem:</p><p><a href=\"https://www.begambleaware.org/\">https://www.begambleaware.org/</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.gamcare.org.uk/\">https://www.gamcare.org.uk/</a></p><p>They can also guide you if you know others with serious gambling problems.</p>',	'2020-04-09 18:13:02',	'2020-07-04 03:34:53'),
