(12,	'Which game manufacturers do you recommend on slot machines?',	'NetEnt, Betsoft, Play n \'Go, Microgaming, Big Time, and Red Tiger are probably the ones that rank highest over the most popular online slot machines these days. Here, it\'s a good idea to try them out in the demo version first, so that you find the games you like the best, rather than thinking about what everyone else is playing.',	'2020-04-14 20:26:31',	'2020-07-31 09:24:24',	NULL,	1),
