>The Legend of Shangri-La Cluster Pays slot machine has a huge jackpot to hunt for. The maximum you can get out of this game is 1 million dollars. Something that must be done with the highest bet of 200$ per spin. Here there are no multipliers or bonus features you need to rake in the big jackpot, but of course, it takes some time. But it is certainly possible to finish with small wins with far fewer stakes as well, as the payback percentage and the re-spin feature is very good in this game.</p>',	NULL,	'The Legend of Shangri-La Cluster Pays Slot',	'96.5%',	'6 x 5',	'0',	'5000',	'Middels',	'0.1$',	'200$',	'https://netent-static.casinomodule.com/games/shangrila_mobile_html/game/shangrila_mobile_html.xhtml?flashParams.bgcolor=000000&gameId=shangrila_not_mobile&mobileParams.lobbyURL=https%3A%2F%2Fgames.netent.com%2Fvideo-slots%2Fshangri-la%2F&server=https%3A%2F%2Fnetent-game.casinomodule.com%2F&lang=en&sessId=DEMO-192686168-EUR&operatorId=netent',	'NetEnt',	'Medium',	'Medium',	'Medium',	'Try the Legend of Shangri-La Slot Machine game for free here!',	'Legend of Shangri-La, online slot',	'Read about all the exciting bonus features at The Legend of Shangri-La Slot Machine. You can also try the game for free here without betting a single penny!',	'2020-04-02 14:29:39',	'2020-07-30 09:19:01');
